<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٩٥٧ - ق ح ل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قحِلَ يَقحَل، قَحْلاً وقَحَلاً، فهو قَحْل وقَحِل<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• قحِلتِ الأرضُ:</span> قحَلَت، يَبِست وأجدبت <span class="c1">"أرض قاحلة"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• قحِل الشَّيخُ:</span> يبس جلدُه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>